      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "LTV analysis on different cohorts for  SP \nand DSP media:\n\n- campaign/keyword/search \nterms/audiences\n- Promotional events, e.g., prime day\n\nTo determine the most efficient \nchannels/marketing mix for acquiring new\ncustomers\n\n(Idea: Giveaway VBA for LTV calculation \nfrom orders report.)",
      "textAlign": "center",
