      "containerId": "HkXEvuez8SupJpDvdqlOT",
      "originalText": "LTV analysis on different cohorts for  SP and DSP media:\n\n- campaign/keyword/search terms/audiences\n- Promotional events, e.g., prime day\n\nTo determine the most efficient channels/marketing mix for acquiring new customers\n\n(Idea: Giveaway VBA for LTV calculation from orders report.)",
